(1, 2, 'Casa de Huéspedes de Encanto a Saint Mamet en el corazón de los Pirineos Franceses', 'Au delà du temps', '<div id="trtext" style="display:block">Usted desea permanecer algunos d&iacute;as en cuartos de hu&eacute;spedes en nuestra regi&oacute;n, a Bagn&egrave;res de Luchon, al coraz&oacute;n de los Pirineos Franceses ?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNuestra casa de hu&eacute;spedes de encanto Au Del&agrave; Du Temps a Saint Mamet, peque&ntilde;o pueblo que toca a Bagn&egrave;res de Luchon, es un lugar tranquilo, lleno de humanidad y de generosidad, frente a la monta&ntilde;a.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEst&aacute; situada a 500 m Termas y El Espacio Forma y Bien Ser de Bagn&egrave;res de Luchon (su Vaporarium es un ba&ntilde;o turco natural y &uacute;nico en Europa).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEn un ambiente confortable y relajante, venga para encontrar el tiempo de recarg&aacute;rsele, de vivir simplemente...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&iexcl; Tres S&eacute;quitos(Apartamentos) entre los que est&aacute;n dos con una peque&ntilde;a cocina de complemento!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLos desayunos copiosos y refinados son servidos en forma de aparador(buffet) entre las 8 horas 30 y las 10 horas.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEn el per&iacute;odo estival (de junio a septiembre) disposici&oacute;n de nuestra piscina exterior calentada (4 x 6 m) de las 14h 30 a las 20h 30, que hay que compartir con nuestros otros inquilinos.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDesolados, pero los animales no son aceptados en nuestros alquileres.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Visite nuestros tres Apartamentos:</h4>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="sayBox">&nbsp;</div>\r\n'),
(2, 2, 'Nuestro Chalé de Montaña con jacuzzi a Portet de Luchon', 'Etch Soulet', '<div align="center"><div id="trtext" style="display:block"><span id="tran0">Chalé "Etch Soulet</span>"<span style="background-color: white;" id="tran1">en el corazón de los Pirineos frenceses</span><b><br><br></b><span id="tran2">Próxima estaciones de esquí de Peyragudes y de Superbagnères</span> - Luchon<br><b><br><span id="result_box" class="" lang="es"><span class="hps">TASA</span> <span class="hps">de un Semana</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">Febrero / Marzo</span> <span class="hps">2014</span>:&nbsp;<span class="hps"> 2990 €</span> <span class="hps">chale</span> <span class="hps">completo</span> <span class="hps">(máximo</span> <span class="hps">22</span> <span class="hps">personas)</span></span></b><br><br><span style="background-color: white;" id="tran3">Posado\r\n a 1265 m de altitud, el sur lleno con vista sobre las montañas, al pie \r\ndel Cuello de Peyresourde, nuestro chalé (280 m²) es uno de los lugares\r\n privilegiados de Luchon, donde usted podrá venir para recargarse en familia o entre amigos en un ambiente montañés pleno de\r\n encanto.</span><br><br><span id="tran4">En el rez de calzada, el apartamento Etch Soulet 1 (100 m ²) puede acoger hasta 8 personas.</span><br><br><span style="background-color: white;" id="tran5">Al\r\n piso, el apartamento Etch soulet 2 (180 m ²) puede acoger, sobre dos \r\nniveles, hasta 14 personas y es equipado de un jacuzzi (interior) para \r\nsiete personas.</span><br><br><span style="background-color: white;" id="tran6">Estos dos apartamentos pueden comunicar entre ellos, si usted lo desea, por una caja de la escalera interior.<br><br><br></span><div align="left"><span style="background-color: white;" id="tran6"></span><b> los animales no son aceptados en nuestros alquileres.</b><br><br><h4>Visite ambos apartamentos del chalé:</h4><span style="background-color: white;" id="tran6"></span></div></div><div class="sayBox">\r\n		        <span class="number-bullet number-bullet-2" title="Directions de traduction"></span> </div><span class="transpan"></span></div><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.homelidays.es/bagneres-de-luchon/chalet-637869es1.htm" target="_blank"> Casa de montaña (madera Piedra) en Bagneres-de-luchon</a>,'),
(1, 3, 'Charming B & B in Saint Mamet in the heart of the Pyrénées', '"Au Delà du Temps"', 'Do you wish to stay a few days in a nice guest house in Bagn&egrave;res de Luchon, in the heart of the French Pyr&eacute;n&eacute;es ?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur charming B &amp; B &quot;Au Del&agrave; Du Temps&quot; is a calm place, full of humanity and generosity in&nbsp; the mountains. We are located in St Mamet , a small village adjacent to Bagn&egrave;res de Luchon.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe house is&nbsp; situated&nbsp; five hundred meters from Luchon&#39;s thermal baths and just a five minute walk from the town centre.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn a confortable and cosy setting, our accomodation gives you the opportunity to relax and unwind...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe have Three Suites for you to choose from. Two of them&nbsp; have a small kitchen so that your stay is cheaper !<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBreakfast, copius and sophisticated, is served as a buffet from 8h30 to 10 h a-m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nin the summer (<em>june to september</em>) our private , heated swimming pool is available for your use from 2.30 pm to 8.30 pm<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring summer holidays, there is a two minimum stay.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nArrival between 4 pm to 7 pm - departure between 9 am to 11 am.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe are sorry but we don&#39;t accept&nbsp; pets.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>&nbsp;visit the Suites:</h4>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n'),
(2, 3, 'Our mountain chalet with a Jacuzzi !', '"Etch Soulet"', '<h3 align="center"><b>-Etch Soulet -&nbsp; at the Heart of the French Pyrénées !</b></h3><p><br></p><p align="center"><b>near the ski stations of Peyragudes and Superbagnères</b></p><p align="center"><b><span id="result_box" class="" lang="en"><span class="hps">RATE</span> <span class="hps">rental</span> <span class="hps">week of February</span> <span class="hps">/</span> <span class="hps">March 2014</span><span>:</span> <span class="hps">€ 2950</span> <span class="hps">full</span> <span class="hps atn">chalet (</span><span class="">max 22</span> <span class="hps">people)</span></span></b></p><p align="center">At a&nbsp; height of 1265 m, near the Peyresourde Col, our chalet is one of thefinest places in the&nbsp; Luchon area, where you can come with family, with goods friends to a cosy muntain atmosphere, full of charm</p><p align="center">On the ground floor, is the Apartment Etch Soulet 1 for 8 persons.</p><p>Above is the Apartment Etch Soulet 2, spilt across two lewels and accomodating up to 14 people. Inside is a relaxing room with a&nbsp; jacuzzi for seven persons.<br></p><p align="left"> These two apartments are linked by an internal staircase. If required, the chalet can be let as one property accomodating up to 22 people.</p><p align="left">Sorry, but pets are not accepted in our property.<br></p><h4 align="left"><b>Visit the Two Apartments of our chalet</b></h4><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.homelidays.co.uk/bagneres-de-luchon/chalet-637869en1.htm" target="_blank"> Holiday rental in Bagneres-de-luchon in Chalet</a>,'),
