(9, 1, 'Etch Soulet 1 (8 personnes)', '<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:HyphenationZone>21</w:HyphenationZone>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther>FR</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignCellWithSp/>\r\n   <w:DontBreakConstrainedForcedTables/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignInTxbx/>\r\n   <w:Word11KerningPairs/>\r\n   <w:CachedColBalance/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <m:mathPr>\r\n   <m:mathFont m:val="Cambria Math"/>\r\n   <m:brkBin m:val="before"/>\r\n   <m:brkBinSub m:val="&#45;-"/>\r\n   <m:smallFrac m:val="off"/>\r\n   <m:dispDef/>\r\n   <m:lMargin m:val="0"/>\r\n   <m:rMargin m:val="0"/>\r\n   <m:defJc m:val="centerGroup"/>\r\n   <m:wrapIndent m:val="1440"/>\r\n   <m:intLim m:val="subSup"/>\r\n   <m:naryLim m:val="undOvr"/>\r\n  </m:mathPr></w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n<p>Un appartement de 100 m&sup2; sur un niveau, jusqu&#39;&agrave; 8 personnes, avec :<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Parking priv&eacute;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Connexion Wi-Fi<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Entr&eacute;e ind&eacute;pendante, au rez-de-chauss&eacute;e du chalet<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Jardin et terrasse privatifs<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Tarifs vacances scolaires F&eacute;vrier et Mars 2014 :</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Etch Soulet 1 (8 personnes) : <strong>1 100 euros / semaine soit 137.50 &euro;/pers pour la semaine</strong></p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>couchages :</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;Trois chambres dont deux chambres avec lit&nbsp; double 160 x 190 et une chambre &quot;dortoir&quot; avec 2 lits superpos&eacute;s adultes soit&nbsp; 4 couchages de 90 x 200<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>description :</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\nUne cuisine - salle &agrave; manger avec cuisini&egrave;re plaques vitroc&eacute;ramiques et four catalyse, four micro-ondes, lave vaisselle, r&eacute;frig&eacute;rateur avec compartiments cong&eacute;lation. Table et chaises pour 8 couverts. 1 chemin&eacute;e.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\nUn Salon: avec canap&eacute;, fauteuils, chaises, t&eacute;l&eacute;viseur avec d&eacute;codeur Tnt, lecteur de Dvd (pensez &agrave; apporter vos films), <strong>connexion</strong> <strong>Wifi </strong>et prise &eacute;thernet (acc&egrave;s haut d&eacute;bit)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUne Salle d&#39;eau : avec douche ( 120 x 120), lavabo, toilette, s&egrave;che serviette &eacute;lectrique, &eacute;tag&egrave;res de rangement<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDeux Toilettes : 1 wc dans la salle d&#39;eau et un wc ind&eacute;pendant.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCellier : Un cumulus &eacute;lectrique 300 litres eau chaude en continue, un lave linge, un s&egrave;che linge, un barbecue, 5 transats, table de jardin en bois pour 8 personnes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Conditions de location:</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nAcompte de r&eacute;servation &agrave; verser &agrave; la signature du contrat de location : 30 % du prix total de la location.<br />\r\nSolde de la location &agrave; verser 30 jours avant votre arriv&eacute;e pour confirmer votre venue.<br />\r\nAttestation d&#39;assurance civile locative &quot;vill&eacute;giature&quot;&agrave; renvoyer 30 jours avant la location.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPaiement: par ch&egrave;que ou virement bancaire; pour les locations de derni&egrave;re minute ( moins de 30 jours): paiement en esp&egrave;ces<br />\r\nCaution de garantie: remise de 600 &euro; par ch&egrave;que , virement bancaire ou en esp&egrave;ces pendant l&#39;&eacute;tat des lieux d&#39;entr&eacute;e. Cette caution sera restitu&eacute;e dans la semaine qui suit votre d&eacute;part si aucune d&eacute;gradation n&#39;a &eacute;t&eacute; constat&eacute; lors de l&#39;&eacute;tat des lieux de sortie.<br />\r\nM&eacute;nage: &agrave; la charge du locataire -&gt; Possibilit&eacute; de prendre notre option M&eacute;nage Fin de S&eacute;jour : + 85 &euro;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>R&egrave;glement int&eacute;rieur:</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nLe nombre d&#39;occupants ne doit pas d&eacute;pass&eacute; le nombre autoris&eacute; &agrave; savoir 8 personnes ( enfants et b&eacute;b&eacute;s inclus)<br />\r\nAfin d&#39;&eacute;viter tout malentendus, le chalet est un lieu paisible, totalement inadapt&eacute; aux f&ecirc;tes estudiantines ou assimil&eacute;es.<br />\r\nL&#39;attestation d&#39;assurance demand&eacute;e doit &ecirc;tre au nom du signataire du contrat.<br />\r\nAucune sous-location ne sera autoris&eacute;e.<br />\r\nLe stationnement de camping car,&nbsp; de m&ecirc;me que l&#39;implantation de toiles de tente est strictement interdit sur la propri&eacute;t&eacute;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em><strong>D&eacute;sol&eacute;s, les animaux ne sont pas accept&eacute;s dans nos locations</strong></em><br />\r\n&nbsp;'),
(9, 2, 'Etch Soulet 1 para 8 personas', 'Apartamento de 100 m2 al piso bajo del Chal&eacute; y que puede acoger hasta 8 personas.<br />\r\nSu entrada es independiente.<br />\r\nJard&iacute;n cercado(cerrado) en terraza.<br />\r\nEstacionamiento posible de tres coches sobre el camino de acceso del chal&eacute;.', '<div id="trtext" style="display:block"><strong>Lechos:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nTres c&aacute;maras entre los que est&aacute;n dos c&aacute;maras con la cama 160 doble x 190 y un c&aacute;mara &quot;dormitorio com&uacute;n&quot; con 2 camas 4 superpuestas adultas x 90 x 200<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Descripci&oacute;n:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nUna cocina - comedor con cocinera placas vitrocer&aacute;micas y horno cataliza, horno microondas, lava vajilla, frigor&iacute;fico con compartimientos congelaci&oacute;n. Mesa y sillas para 8 cubiertos. 1 chimenea.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUn Sal&oacute;n: con sof&aacute;, butacas, sillas, televisor con decodificador Tnt, lector de Dvds (piense aportar sus pel&iacute;culas), <strong>Wifi</strong> y toma &eacute;thernet (acceso de alta velocidad)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUn Aseo: con ducha (120 x 120), lavabo, aseo(traje), seca toallas el&eacute;ctrico, estanter&iacute;as de arreglo<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDos Aseos(Trajes): 1 excusado en el aseo y un excusado independiente.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBodega: un c&uacute;mulo el&eacute;ctrico 300 litros continuamente, uno lava ropa blanca, una secadora de ropa, una barbacoa, 5 regatas trasantl&aacute;nticas, una mesa de jard&iacute;n de madera para 8 personas.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="sayBox">&nbsp;</div>\r\n'),
(9, 3, 'Etch Soulet 1 ( 8 pers )', 'Apartment of 100 m&sup2; at the ground floor of the Chalet and being able to welcome up to 8 persons.<br />\r\nIndependent entrance.<br />\r\nGarden enclosed outside(in terrace).<br />\r\nPossibility to park three cars on the access road of the chalet.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '<strong>Sleepings around:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;Three bedrooms:</strong> two bedrooms with double bed 160 x 190 and one bedroom &quot;dormitory&quot; with 2 adults bunk beds&nbsp; 4 x 90 x 200<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Description: </strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>A kitchen</strong> - dining room with cook stick vitreous ceramics and oven catalyses, oven microwave, washes dishes, refrigerator with compartments freezing. Table and chairs for 8 flatware. 1 fireplace.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>A Lounge</strong>: with sofa, armchairs, chairs, television set with decoder Tnt, DVD drive (think of bringing your movies),<strong> WiFi</strong> and &eacute;thernet grip(taking) ( broadband access)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>A Shower-room</strong>: with shower (120 x 120), washbasin, 1wc,&nbsp; electric towel dryer, shelves of arrangement<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Two water closed </strong>: 1 wc in the shower-room and one&nbsp; independent&#39;s wc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Storeroom</strong>: an electric cumulus continuous 300 liters, a washing machine, a tumble-dryer, a barbecue, 5 deckchairs, wooden garden table for 8 persons.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Rental &#39;s Conditions: </strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nDeposit of reservation to be paid by bank transfer at the signature of the rental agreement: 30 % of the total price of the rent.<br />\r\nPay(Balance) of the rent to be paid by bank transfer 30 days before your arrival to confirm your coming.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPayment: by&nbsp; bank transfer; for the last-minute rents ( less than 30 days): payment in cash<br />\r\nPledge of guarantee: put back(handed) by 640 &euro; by&nbsp; bank transfer or in cash during the current situation(inventory of fixtures) of entrance. This pledge will be restored in the week which follows your departure if no damages was not noticed in the current situation(inventory of fixtures) of exit(release).<br />\r\nHousework: chargeable to the tenant - Possibility of taking our option housework at the End of Stay: + 105 euro<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Internal rules:</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe number of occupants does not&nbsp; exceeded the number authorized : <strong>8 persons (children and inclusive babies)</strong><br />\r\nTo avoid quite misunderstandings, the chalet is a peaceful place, totally unsuitable for the student or assimilated parties.<br />\r\nNone under rent will be authorized.<br />\r\nThe campingcar , as well as the setting-up of tent canvases is forbidden on the property.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Sorry but pets are not accepted in our rents</strong></u>'),
