 euros / semaine</strong> soit 153.57 &euro;/pers pour la semaine', 'Entr&eacute;e :<strong> </strong>lave linge et s&egrave;che linge &agrave; condensation, r&eacute;frig&eacute;rateur avec compartiment cong&eacute;lation, portant et porte manteaux.<br />\r\nJacuzzi 7 places assises.<br />\r\nCuisine et salle &agrave; manger:<strong> </strong>cuisine &eacute;quip&eacute;e avec &eacute;vier deux bacs, plan de travail, quatre plaques &eacute;lectriques, un four standard &agrave; pyrolyse,une hotte aspirante, un r&eacute;frig&eacute;rateur et cong&eacute;lateur, une table pour 14 couverts ( possibilit&eacute; rajouter table suppl&eacute;mentaire), meubles de rangements pour vaisselle et couverts, un lave vaisselle. Deux services &agrave; raclette sont &agrave; votre disposition. Le nombre de couverts est largement pr&eacute;vu pour 14 personnes.<br />\r\nUne premi&egrave;re salle de bain<strong> </strong>avec petite baignoire et douchette, s&egrave;che serviette &eacute;lectrique, lavabo.<br />\r\nUne chambre<strong> </strong>avec lit double 160 x 190, fauteuil, &eacute;tag&egrave;res, penderie.<br />\r\nToilette ind&eacute;pendante.<br />\r\nSalon avec chemin&eacute;e, t&eacute;l&eacute;vision Tnt &eacute;cran plat et d&eacute;codeur Orange par satellite, fauteuils, canap&eacute;, balcon ext&eacute;rieur. <strong>connexion Wifi </strong><br />\r\nUne chambre avec lit double de 160 x 190, armoire avec penderie, chaise, tables de chevet<br />\r\nEscalier.<br />\r\nUne chambre avec lit double de 160 x 190, commode, penderie, chaise, tables de chevet.<br />\r\nUne salle d&#39;eau avec douche, lavabo, s&egrave;che serviette &eacute;lectrique.<br />\r\nUne chambre<strong> </strong>dortoir avec quatre lits simples de 90 x 190, meubles de rangement , une penderie.<br />\r\nUne chambre avec lit double avec un lit double de 160 x 190, &eacute;tag&egrave;res, chaises, portants, tables de chevet.<br />\r\nUne petite chambre avec un&nbsp; lit double de 160 x 190, table de chevet.<br />\r\nToilette ind&eacute;pendante.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&agrave; l&#39;ext&eacute;rieur: jardin pentu; cabanon faisant office de local &agrave; skis et&nbsp; rangement pour barbecue, transats.<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; table de jardin ext&eacute;rieure en teck.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Conditions de location:</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nAcompte de r&eacute;servation &agrave; verser &agrave; la signature du contrat de location : 30 % du prix total de la location.<br />\r\nSolde de la location &agrave; verser 30 jours avant votre arriv&eacute;e pour confirmer votre venue.<br />\r\nAttestation d&#39;assurance civile locative &quot;vill&eacute;giature&quot;&agrave; renvoyer 30 jours avant la location.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPaiement: par ch&egrave;que ou virement bancaire; pour les locations de derni&egrave;re minute ( moins de 30 jours): paiement en esp&egrave;ces<br />\r\nCaution de garantie: remise de 1600 &euro; par ch&egrave;que , virement bancaire ou en esp&egrave;ces pendant l&#39;&eacute;tat des lieux d&#39;entr&eacute;e. Cette caution sera restitu&eacute;e dans la semaine qui suit votre d&eacute;part si aucune d&eacute;gradation n&#39;a &eacute;t&eacute; constat&eacute; lors de l&#39;&eacute;tat des lieux de sortie.<br />\r\nM&eacute;nage: &agrave; la charge du locataire -&gt; Possibilit&eacute; de prendre notre option M&eacute;nage Fin de S&eacute;jour : + 105 &euro;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>R&egrave;glement int&eacute;rieur:</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nLe nombre d&#39;occupants ne doit pas d&eacute;pass&eacute; le nombre autoris&eacute; &agrave; savoir 14 personnes ( enfants et b&eacute;b&eacute;s inclus)<br />\r\nAfin d&#39;&eacute;viter tout malentendus, le chalet est un lieu paisible, totalement inadapt&eacute; aux f&ecirc;tes estudiantines ou assimil&eacute;es.<br />\r\nL&#39;attestation d&#39;assurance demand&eacute;e doit &ecirc;tre au nom du signataire du contrat.<br />\r\nAucune sous-location ne sera autoris&eacute;e.<br />\r\nLe stationnement de camping car,&nbsp; de m&ecirc;me que l&#39;implantation de toiles de tente est interdit sur la propri&eacute;t&eacute;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em><strong>D&eacute;sol&eacute;s, mais les animaux ne sont pas accept&eacute;s dans nos locations</strong></em><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;'),
(10, 2, 'Etch Soulet 2 para 14 personas ', '&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nEtch Soulet 2<br />\r\n<br />\r\nApartamento de 180m &sup2; pudiendo acoger hasta 14 personas (ni&ntilde;os y beb&eacute;s incluidos).<br />\r\nEl apartamento est&aacute; situado en el primer y segund piso del chal&eacute; con una entrada independiente y de llano pie.<br />\r\nPosee una sala de relajaci&oacute;n con un spa de 7 sitios.<br />\r\nUn jard&iacute;n cercado es a su disposici&oacute;n as&iacute; como una terraza y un balc&oacute;n.<br />\r\nAparcamiento privado para tres coches contra altura del chal&eacute;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div><strong>una semana en febrero / marzo de 2014, el precio de la semana es &euro; 2.990 para el chalet entero</strong></div>\r\n', '&nbsp;<br />\r\nEntrada: lava ropa blanca y secadora de ropa a condensaci&oacute;n; sustentador y lleva abrigos.<br />\r\nSpa: jacuzzi 7 sitios(plazas) Marca a SunBelt.<br />\r\nCocina y comedor: equipada cocina con fregadero dos cubas, plan de trabajo, cuatro placas el&eacute;ctricas, un horno est&aacute;ndar a pirolisis, un cu&eacute;vano aspirante, un frigor&iacute;fico y un congelador, una mesa para 14 cubiertos (posibilidad a&ntilde;adir mesa suplementaria), amueblas de arreglos para vajilla y cubiertos, uno lava vajilla. Dos servicios a raspador son a su disposici&oacute;n. El n&uacute;mero de cubiertos est&aacute; ampliamente previsto para 14 personas.<br />\r\nUna primera sala de ba&ntilde;o con peque&ntilde;a ba&ntilde;era y douchette, seca toallas el&eacute;ctrico, lavabo.<br />\r\nUn c&aacute;mara con la cama 160 doble x 190, butaca, estanter&iacute;as, guardarropa.<br />\r\nAseo(Traje) independiente.Sal&oacute;n con chimenea, t&eacute;l&eacute;vison Tnt pantalla llano y decodificador ADSL por sat&eacute;lite, butacas, sof&aacute;, balc&oacute;n exterior.<br />\r\nUn c&aacute;mara con la cama doble de 160 x 190, armario con guardarropa, silla, mesillas de noche<br />\r\nEscalera.<br />\r\nUn c&aacute;mara con la cama doble de 160 x 190, c&oacute;moda, guardarropa, silla, mesillas de noche.<br />\r\nUn aseo con ducha, lavabo, seca toallas el&eacute;ctrico.<br />\r\nUn c&aacute;mara dormitorio com&uacute;n con cuatro camas simples de 90 x 190, amueblas de arreglo, un guardarropa.<br />\r\nUn c&aacute;mara con la cama doble con la cama doble de 160 x 190, estanter&iacute;as, sillas, sustentadores, mesillas de noche.<br />\r\nUn peque&ntilde;o c&aacute;mara con la cama doble de 160 x 190, mesilla de noche.<br />\r\nAseo(Traje) independiente.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPor fuera: jard&iacute;n inclinado; casa de campo que hace las veces de local a esqu&iacute;s y arreglo para barbacoa, regatas trasantl&aacute;nticas.<br />\r\nMesa<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Condiciones de alquiler:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnticipo de reserva que hay que pagar a la firma del contrato de arrendamiento: el 30 % del precio total del alquiler.<br />\r\nSueldo del alquiler que hay que pagar 30 d&iacute;as antes de su llegada para confirmar su llegada.<br />\r\nPago: por transferencia bancaria; para los alquileres de &uacute;ltimo minuto (menos de 30 d&iacute;as): pago en met&aacute;lico<br />\r\nFianza de garant&iacute;a: devuelta por 1600 euros en met&aacute;lico durante el estado de los lugares de entrada. Esta fianza ser&aacute; restituida si ningunas degradaciones ha sido comprobado en el estado de los lugares de salida.<br />\r\nLimpieza: al cargo del inquilino - Posibilidad de tomar nuestra opci&oacute;n Cuida Fin de Estancia: + 105&euro;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Reglamento interior:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nEl n&uacute;mero de ocupantes no debe sobrepasado el n&uacute;mero autorizado a saber a 14 personas (ni&ntilde;os y beb&eacute;s incluidos)<br />\r\nCon el fin de evitar totalmente malentendidos, el chal&eacute; es un lugar apacible, totalmente inadaptado a las fiestas estudiantiles o asimiladas.<br />\r\nEl certificado de seguridad(seguro) solicitada debe ser en nombre del signatario del contrato.<br />\r\nNinguno bajo alquiler ser&aacute; autorizada.<br />\r\nEl estacionamiento de camping car, lo mismo que la implantaci&oacute;n de telas de tienda es prohibida sobre la propiedad.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>Desolados pero los animales no son aceptados en nuestros alquileres</em><br />\r\n&nbsp;'),
(10, 3, 'Etch Soulet 2 (14 pers)', '&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Etch Soulet 2</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>This Apartment of 180m &sup2; is being able to receive 14 persons (children and inclusive babies).</strong><br />\r\n<strong>The apartment is situated in the 1st and 2nd floor of the chalet with an independent entrance and the high tide foot. There is a relaxing room with a seven seat jacuzzi.<br />\r\nA garden enclosed at your disposal, terrace and balcony. Parking for three small cars&nbsp; is against top of the chalet.</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div><strong>&nbsp;February 15th / March 15th&nbsp; 2014,&nbsp; the rate rental for one week ( sathurday to sathurday)&nbsp; is 2990 euro for the whole chalet</strong></div>\r\n', '<strong>Entrance / Airlocks:</strong> washing machine and condensation tumble-dryer; carrying and carry(wear) coats.<br />\r\n<strong>Spa:</strong> Jacuzzi 7 places Marks SunBelt.<br />\r\n<strong>Kitchen</strong> and dining room: fully-equipped kitchen with kitchen sink two tubs, work plan, four electric plates(patches), a standard oven with pyrolysis, an extractor fan, a refrigerator and freezer, a table for 14 persons (possibility add additional table), storage furniture for dishes and flatware, one washes dishes. Two services with raclette are at your disposal. The number of flatware is widely planned for 14 persons.<br />\r\n<strong>A bathroom</strong> with small bathtub and shower head, electric towel dryer, washbasin.<br />\r\n<strong>A bedroom</strong> with double bed 160 x 190, armchair, shelves, closet.<br />\r\n<strong>Lounge </strong>with fireplace, t&eacute;l&eacute;vison Tnt, Flat screen and ADSL decoder by satellite, armchairs, sofa, outside balcony. <strong>WIFI</strong><br />\r\n<strong>A bedroom</strong> with double bed&nbsp; 160 x 190, cupboard with closet, chair, bedside tables<br />\r\nStaircase.<br />\r\n<strong>A bedroom</strong> with double bed&nbsp; 160 x 190, chest of drawers, closet, chair, bedside tables.<br />\r\n<strong>A shower-room</strong> with shower, washbasin, electric towel dryer.<br />\r\n<strong>A bedroom &quot;dormitory&quot;</strong> with four single beds of 90 x 190, storage furniture, a closet.<br />\r\n<strong>A bedroom</strong> with double bed 160 x 190, shelves, chairs, carrying, bedside tables.<br />\r\n<strong>A bedroom</strong> with a double bed of 160 x 190, bedside table.<br />\r\n<strong>2 independents water closets</strong> .<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOutdoor: sloping garden; small house acting as premises(place) with skis and arrangement for barbecue, deckchairs(transatlantic races).<br />\r\nOutside garden table<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Rental &#39;s Conditions: </strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Deposit of reservation</strong> to be paid by bank transfer <strong>at the signature of the rental</strong> <strong> agreement</strong>: 30 % of the total price of the rent.<br />\r\nPay <strong>Balance&nbsp;</strong> of the rent to be paid by bank transfer <strong>30 days before your arrival</strong> to confirm your coming.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPayment: by&nbsp; bank transfer; for the last-minute rents ( less than 30 days): payment in cash<br />\r\n<strong>Pledge of guarantee</strong>: put back(handed) by 1600 &euro; by&nbsp; bank transfer or in cash during the inventory of entrance. This pledge will be restored in the week which follows your departure if no damages was not noticed in the current situation(inventory of fixtures) of exit(release).<br />\r\nHousework: chargeable to the tenant - Possibility of taking our option housework at the End of Stay: + 105 euro for this apartment<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Internal rules:</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe number of occupants does not&nbsp; exceeded the number authorized : <strong>14 persons (children and inclusive babies)</strong><br />\r\nTo avoid quite misunderstandings, the chalet is a peaceful place, totally unsuitable for the student or assimilated parties.<br />\r\nNone under rent will be authorized.<br />\r\nThe campingcar , as well as the setting-up of tent canvases is forbidden on the property.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Sorry but pets are not accepted in our rents</strong>'),
